    "plan_content": "The plan covers four files across two crates:\n\n1. **`crates/uv-cli/src/lib.rs`** – Add `Stats(StatsArgs)` variant to `CacheCommand` enum and a new `StatsArgs` struct (mirrors `SizeArgs` exactly).\n2. **`crates/uv/src/commands/cache_stats.rs`** – New file that iterates `CacheBucket::iter()`, computes per-bucket disk usage via `DiskUsage`, prints each bucket's size, then a `total:` line. Supports `--human` flag.\n3. **`crates/uv/src/commands/mod.rs`** – Declare `mod cache_stats;` and re-export `cache_stats::cache_stats`.\n4. **`crates/uv/src/lib.rs`** – Add dispatch arm for `CacheCommand::Stats(args)` following the existing `Size` pattern.",
